{"tid":1188861,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實達哥一早表咗態","createTime":"2019-06-06T13:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T14:21:01.000Z","uid":251052,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9065e9a4698ae4b0e953c5b727253b830cdb541e","tid":1188861,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"香港殿堂級樂隊 向來敢言<br />\n達哥一路走黎始終如一 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kZaE6jAwOM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkZaE6jAwOM4&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BglUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=fd5af866\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kZaE6jAwOM4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕    作曲：劉以達 <br />\n<br />\n舊日或問天 怎允許摧毀信念<br />\n浩蕩像為了 被懷念<br />\n現在別問他 可有膽公開紀念<br />\n被現實騎劫 怎怨天<br />\n<br />\n如燭光都有罪 將暗黑多幾十年<br />\n如傷疤都有靈 未變臉<br />\n回憶即使有罪 真相怎麼敢無言<br />\n歷史假使有人 定被發現<br />\n<br />\n現在若問他 可悔當天走太前<br />\n道路腐壞了 不敢涉險<br />\n現在若問我 怎會這麼想紀念<br />\n烈焰幻滅過 總有煙<br />\n<br />\n如燭光都有罪 將暗黑多幾十年<br />\n如傷疤都有靈 未變臉<br />\n回憶即使有罪 真相怎麼敢無言<br />\n歷史假使有人 定被發現<br />\n<br />\n皇天不必答辯 只怕蒼生肯忘言<br />\n后土不知冷熱 生滅無念<br />\n歷史只懂向前 輾轉反側三十年<br />\n如今滄桑少年 莫問蒼天<br />\n<br />\n若舉傘 為誰命運祭奠<br />\n廣場上 這麼多告別<br />\n莫須有 是誰造就壯烈<br />\n願廣場上 聲音不會滅"},{"pid":"6c32da9bc5acaaf045076c20cdff9bf3d6481c88","tid":1188861,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64179535baa6d1b8e369f579d95e852995161bb0","tid":1188861,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c32da9bc5acaaf045076c20cdff9bf3d6481c88","tid":1188861,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:01:42.000Z","msg":"達哥為公義發聲 完全唔驚比人封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65d456507899f586ede3363b0ff60d528e06776","tid":1188861,"uid":3429